o_description: Worldview Education Fair is dedicated to helping institutions recruit prospective international students from South Africa. This fair is open to all institutions worldwide, helping you meet and recruit a wide pool of quality potential students. Many fairs and exhibitions focus only on recruiters from a specific country, thereby attracting a limited pool of students with predetermined interests in those specific study destinations. The Worldview Education Fair brings institutions from all around the world to one place; giving students more opportunities and options, thereby attracting a larger, more diverse pool of students.
